_sText:
This is a map with differents playable stages. The first one (A) is a knife map, the second one (B) is a deagle map, and finally, map from AWP (C). Also, I thought for thouse players who are AFK, so from the T base from map C you can go to CT base and vice-versa. When you enter to the other room again, A or B, your weapons will be striped and you will have to get again your weapons.

Enjoy it :D
